  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Phoneme
    Phoneme class used to calculate the confusion costs contains getters and setters for the different categories derived from IPA table.
    PhonemeContainer
    used by the phoneme creator to store phoneme sequences
    PhonemeCreator
    class used to convert graphemes to phonemes.
    PhonemeDB
    containes the stored phonemes (used by phoneme creator)
    PhonemePair
    utility class
    PhonemeSubstitution
    containes the 0.1/0.9, Derived IPA and Google Revers Heuristic used to calculate substitution scores
